{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"readonly","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgress","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@MLNOfflinePackProgress","text":"MLNOfflinePackProgress","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"progress","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The progress of an inactive or completed pack is computed lazily, and all its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"fields are set to 0 by default. To request the pack’s progress, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-requestProgress"},{"type":"text","text":" method. To get notified when the progress becomes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"known and when it changes, observe KVO change notifications on this pack’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" key path. Alternatively, you can add an observer for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification"},{"type":"text","text":"s about this pack that come from the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"default notification center."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/progress","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"abstract":[{"text":"The pack’s current progress.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/progress"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"progress","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"progress","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(py)progress","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"text":"progress","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePack"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"},{"type":"text","text":" represents a collection of resources necessary for viewing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a region offline to a local database."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack","role":"symbol","title":"MLNOfflinePack"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack/progress":{"abstract":[{"text":"The pack’s current progress.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","title":"progress","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/progress","fragments":[{"text":"progress","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/progress"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackProgress":{"title":"MLNOfflinePackProgress","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackprogress","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgress","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A structure containing information about an offline pack’s current download"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"progress."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackProgress"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflineStorage"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"MLNOfflineStorage implements a singleton (shared object) that manages offline"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"title":"MLNOfflineStorage","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification":{"title":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackprogresschangednotification","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Posted by the shared "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage"},{"type":"text","text":" object when an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object’s progress changes. The progress may change due to a resource being"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"downloaded or because the pack discovers during the download that more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"resources are required for offline viewing. This notification is posted"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"whenever any field in the "},{"code":"progress","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property changes."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","role":"symbol"}}}